edu.umn.biomedicus.numbers

Class NumberModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umn.biomedicus.numbers.NumberModel

  • public class NumberModel
extends Object
    Stores information about English numeral words and the mappings from those words to their decimal forms. It is used by other classes in this package to perform work.

    This class is immutable so it is thread-safe.

    Since:
    1.0.0
